caption: From the far end of a large room, you hear rustling, ducks quacking, water splashing, followed by a conversation between an adult female and male, along with duck calls being blown.
In a large room, applause, a man's yell, and group singing can be heard.
In the distance of a large room, a man speaks intermittently over the tapping of a keyboard.
In the front of a large room, you hear a motor running, followed by a honking horn and a wailing siren.
The sound of an airplane engine is coming from the distant end of a large, echoey room.
A continuous beeping sound is coming from a machine located at the far back of a mid-sized room.
A sound of wind blowing followed by a zoom emanates from the far right side of the large room.
A woman's laughter accompanies an infant's cries from the far end of the large room.
In the back of a large room, leaves rustle, a small bell chimes, and birds chirp in the background.
